reviewText: Love this movie its raunchy, creepy, freaky and disturbing in the best way possible. Benji played the crap out of his role!

One ugly little weirdo of a film, but poignant in an underbelly sort of way. Interesting story with an unexpected twist at the end. I would definitely recommend it, but what can I say? My kid is in it!
Okay movie but not very good acting. It also had a very amateur quality to it. It looked interesting - I guess I was fooled by the description and trailer.
